i can't believe its over!!!!! but im excited to get my summer started!!

hawaii is absolutely beautiful...like everything u imagine! 

we went to waikiki on oahu and it was so busy! but fun...and AMAZING shopping.....burberry, (4 coach stores), fendi, macys... but i didn't do a lot of shoppin! and we went to waimea bay which was my fave and the water was sooo clear, like i stood on this cliff thing and looked down and u could see the white sand on the bottom! and there was like no seaweed or ne thing....so i jumped off it!! and it was the most fun ever. and we went to the north shore and the drive was sooooo beautiful! 

then we went to maui and to a luau and i tried OCTAPUS! ahh! it was yucky. and we just stayed at the hotel all week. and the waves on this beach were UNBELEIVABLE....like u couldn't walk into the ocean w/o gettin knocked over, they were so powerful and big and so much fun! and we went on atv's all over this mouatain thing and that was funnnnn.

OMG we went snorkeling at this one place, and 45 MINUTES before we got there someone DIED there!! and i just can't snorkel cuz its scary  cuz ur like a foot over these big coral things w/ fish swimmin around and i just couldn't do it! annnd wen we were in oahu, there all these tiger shark warnings in maui...like a bunch swam up to shore. annnd like 2 people got lost at sea after being on jet skis for a few days (but then found). so it was a lil scary!

but it was soo cool cuz we were on one of the beaches, and if u looked out, could see a bunch of dolphins swimmin and like jumpin outta the water!! it was crazy!!!

and i just love my friends soooooo much and missed them a TON! and i just really have the best friends ever, they all just make me happy...just wen i talk to them! and i love em!

(and ill put up some pics later!) ALOOOOOHA

so will someone just decide for me! i feel like i need to decide tonight, i hate not having a plan or w/e and i just love too much stuff and i gotta look at colleges this summer...AAAHHHHHH!!!

5 weeks and 7 days until 
 
S  U  M  M  E  R
 
      & H  A  W  A  I  I!!

I'm So excited!

My sister came home this weekend and i'm so happy bout that, not just cuz i get to use her car and wear her clothes, but i love hangin out w/ my sisters.

But i decided i should probably get a job, cuz i really need money right now! b/c i really need to get some summery clothes for hawaii...ahh, shopping, it brings up a sensitive subject for me (i just bought some super cute shoes last week, and they're on sale this week!!!)

I am just so ready for this year to be over, even though i've loved this year a ton and don't want senior year to come (cuz it'll go by too fast), but i just can't take all the work! it's soo frustrating, and i just don't want to do it...at all.

So i was goin thru some pretty hard times and prayed to God that he would help me thru wat i was going thru, and the next day i cam across this...

    "When i want to do good, evil is right there with me. For in my inner being I delight in God's Law; but i see another law at work in the members of my body, waging war against the law of my mind and making me a prisoner of the law of sin at work within my members. What a wretched man I am! Who will rescue me from this body of death? Thanks be to God - Through Jesus Christ our Lord!" Romans 7.

...it's pretty sweet wat a little prayer can do.
